<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fórum Tribunal Federativo</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/flowbite@3.1.2/dist/flowbite.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-900">
<header>
<nav class="bg-white border-gray-200 px-4 lg:px-6 py-2.5 dark:bg-gray-800">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center mx-auto max-w-screen-xl">
        <a href="#" class="flex items-center">
            <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f3/Justice_scale_icon.svg/2048px-Justice_scale_icon.svg.png" class="mr-3 h-8" alt="Tribunal Logo" />
            <span class="self-center text-xl font-semibold whitespace-nowrap dark:text-white">Fórum Tribunal Federativo</span>
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center lg:order-2">
            <a href="#" class="text-white bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-blue-300 font-medium rounded-lg text-sm px-4 py-2 dark:bg-blue-600 dark:hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none dark:focus:ring-blue-800">Área do Servidor</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden justify-between items-center w-full lg:flex lg:w-auto lg:order-1">
            <ul class="flex flex-col mt-4 font-medium lg:flex-row lg:space-x-8 lg:mt-0">
                <li><a href="#" class="nav-link">Início</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="nav-link">Serviços</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="nav-link">Processos</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="nav-link">Consulta Pública</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="nav-link">Contato</a></li>
                <li><a href="#" class="nav-link">Login</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>
</header>

<section class="py-12">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl px-4 mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Bem-vindo ao Portal do Fórum Tribunal Federativo</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Aqui você encontra acesso a informações processuais, serviços jurídicos, agendamento de audiências, consulta de andamentos e muito mais.</p>
    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
      <a href="#" class="btn-primary">Consultar Processo</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn-outline">Solicitar Certidão</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl px-4 mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Atendimento ao Cidadão</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Informações sobre funcionamento, agendamentos e como acessar os serviços do fórum.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Audiências e Prazos</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Veja o calendário de audiências e os prazos processuais em vigor.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-white mb-2">Serviços Online</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Emita certidões, faça peticionamento eletrônico e acesse informações sobre processos em andamento.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="bg-gray-800 py-6 mt-12">
  <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 text-center text-white">
    <p>&copy; 2025 Fórum Tribunal Federativo. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
.nav-link {
    display: block;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    color: #4B5563;
    text-decoration: none;
}
.nav-link:hover {
    color: #1D4ED8;
}
.btn-primary {
    background-color: #1D4ED8;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.2s;
}
.btn-primary:hover {
    background-color: #2563EB;
}
.btn-outline {
    border: 2px solid #1D4ED8;
    color: #1D4ED8;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.2s;
}
.btn-outline:hover {
    background-color: #1D4ED8;
    color: white;
}
</style>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/flowbite@3.1.2/dist/flowbite.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
